<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٥٣٩ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3997">عَبْدُ اللهِ بْنُ يُوسُفَ: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5361">مَالِكٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3384">عَبْدِ الرَّحْمَنِ بْنِ الْقَاسِمِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5159">أَبِيهِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3026">عَائِشَةَ </a><span class="special">﵂</span> زَوْجِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>،<span class="c5"> قَالَتْ:</span> <span class="c2">«كُنْتُ أُطَيِّبُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٣٧⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رَسُولَ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> لِإِحْرَامِهِ حِينَ يُحْرِمُ، وَلِحِلِّهِ قَبْلَ أَنْ يَطُوفَ بِالْبَيْتِ».<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>